title: Yulia Skripal released from the hospital: media
text:
Yulia Skripal released from the hospital 4:17am EDT - 01:12 
The daughter of former Russian double agent Sergei Skripal, Yulia, has reportedly been released from the hospital after recovering from the alleged nerve agent attack on them. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
